                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">
                        <gloss type="from">Acting British consul-general</gloss> to <gloss type="to"
                            >United States legation</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tabriz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-04-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 17, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 6.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>Bagdasarian has reached and is still a prisoner. Emir-i-Nizam appears to take no
                    notice of instructions sent him. I shall take measures to-morrow and report.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
